                    <img src="images/kuka-robot.jpg" alt="KUKA Robot">
                    <p><strong>Overview:</strong> Integration of a KUKA robot with Siemens PLC to develop a fully automated pick and place application. The system improves efficiency and precision in industrial automation processes, where the robot picks up items from a conveyor belt and places them in designated locations.</p>
